Package: RMAnno
Type: Package
Title: A Tool for the Annotation of RNA Modification Data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Data: 2022-12-29
Authors@R: 
    person(given  = "Jiongming",
           family = "Ma",
           role   = c("aut", "cre"),
           email  = "jiongming.ma@outlook.com")
Maintainer: Jiongming Ma <jiongming.ma@outlook.com>
Depends: R (>= 4.1)
Description: A tool for the annotation of RNA modification data.
    This package can help users to annotate RNA methylation sites and peaks more 
    conveniently. It could annotate the positive and negative strand information 
    separately and simultaneously display all the site's information in the 
    overlapping gene region, thereby preventing incorrect and missing annotation 
    of gene names. RMAnno also provides various information annotations to provide 
    users with relevant functional hints for potential interactions with RNA 
    methylation.
